  "instructions": [
    "Heat a salt block to 400°F.",
    "Spread the vegan garlic spread evenly over the pita bread.",
    "Sprinkle the namul blanch season over the garlic spread.",
    "Add the chopped parsley, sliced scallions, red bell pepper, and cucumber on top of the pita bread.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Place the salt block in the oven and cook for 2 minutes, or until the vegetables are slightly softened.",
    "Remove the wrap from the oven and let it cool for 1 minute.",
    "Fold the pita bread in half to enclose the filling and serve hot."
